  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Legendary%20Wukong.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Finally, at 1st level, while your wrath is a powerful tool you use to win battles, it can also be a detriment that can be used against those you love, meaning that you need a way to freely disapate that anger.</p><p>You gain a new item known as the <em><strong>Control Mechanism (CM)</strong></em>. The flavor for this item is up to the player/DM and can be anything from a shock collar to a magical crown. The CM has a number of charges equal to half your proficiency bonus per rest. Anytime you are under the Berserk condition, you may spend 1 charge to clear yourself of any number of ranks of Berserk. For each rank of Berserk you clear as a result of this item, you gain +5 Temporary Hit Points until the end of the current combat.</p><p></p>",
